### Get an app

```
Example Request
```

```shell
curl "https://api.example.org/v3/apps/[guid]" \
  -X GET \
  -H "Authorization: bearer [token]"
```

```
Example Response
```

```http
HTTP/1.1 200 OK
Content-Type: application/json

<%= yield_content :single_app %>
```

#### Definition
`GET /v3/apps/:guid`

#### Query parameters

Name | Type | Description
---- | ---- | ------------
**include** | _string_ | **Experimental** - Optionally include additional related resources in the response. <br>Valid values are `space`, `space.organization`, and `processes`. Multiple includes are comma-delimited.

